import React from 'react'
import { Row,Col } from 'react-bootstrap'
import Product from '../components/Product'
import products from '../products'
const Home = () => {
    
    return (
        <>
        <Row>
            {products.map(product=>(
                <Col key={product.id}>
                <Product product={product} />
                </Col>
            ))}                          
        </Row>  
        </>
    )
}

export default Home
